data.description: An Exceptional Gem in Timber Springs: This immaculate home, better than new, offers a large kitchen with eat-in space, shiplap backsplash, and a stylish island. The open floor plan seamlessly connects to a great room adorned with a shiplap fireplace, complemented by stunning 3/4 sand-finished hardwood throughout the main level. Upstairs, an oversized master suite and two additional bedrooms, all with walk-in closets, provide ample space for your family. The master bathroom is a retreat in itself, boasting a tile shower, double vanities, and a relaxing soaking tub. The bonus room over the garage offers versatility for your needs. Step outside and savor the covered back porch, with scenic view of mature trees and no rear neighbors. No HOA and convenience to I-24, the Military base, shopping, and dining establishments make this home an opportunity you can't miss. Sellers are offering $14,000 in concessions with a full price offer.
